Bibtech is the brave new Bibtex for Mediawiki

=== USAGE EXAMPLE ===
Lorem Ipsum is simply dummy {{#btref: ENTRY_CKEY}} text of the 
...
<bibtech ARGS>
VALID BIBTEX
</bibtech>

ENTRY_CKEY is from the bibtex database

=== ARGS ===
src="FILE"
read the database from Bibtech/bib/FILE instead

style="STYLE"
use the style from Bibtech/sty/STYLE (.php and .css)


